# JQuery Mobile Metro

This is an experimental Grails project using Metro UI HTML5-based theme on top of JQuery Mobile that mimics Windows Phone 7 native look and feel.  This project is based on the [sgrebnov's JQMobile-Metro-Theme github project](https://github.com/sgrebnov/jqmobile-metro-theme).

## Demo

[Check out the demo](http://jqm-metro-test.cloudfoundry.com) on Cloud Foundry.  

## Installation

You can use the [template project](https://github.com/zachlendon/jquery-mobile-metro-grails-test) as your guide or run:

grails install-plugin jquery-mobile-metro